<%# Canonical rendering of an @mention. Used both as the Action Text attachment
    partial (stored messages) and as the Lexxy editor representation, so the
    pill looks identical while composing and after sending. The `mention` class
    + data-mention-employee-id let the conversation controller flag the viewer's
    own mentions per-viewer (a shared server broadcast can't bake that in). %>
<span class="mention font-medium text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400"
      data-mention-employee-id="<%= employee.id %>">@<%= employee.handle %></span>
